Internal Auditor - Required for a Large Group
An Internal Auditor is required for a large group within the UAE.
Bachelors Degree or above, that is Business Related
Relevant Qualifications; CA, CPA, ACCA, CIA, etc.
Experience:
•	2 to 3 years Internal Audit Experience
•	Having Engineering or Construction experience, preferred.
Skills:
•	Knowledge of current auditing practices and standards
•	Plan, Prepare and Perform Audits
•	Computer skills
Florence International Consulting is an executive search company based in Dubai, focusing on the GCC. We specialize in Audit, Engineering, Finance, HR, IT and Risk.
